{"tid":1537494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 升級行動] 太子831懷疑命案除左玩程序仲可以做咩?","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:16:56.000Z","uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c97c5529c29679cb34411c02ab33785d460283f4","tid":1537494,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係死左人，我唔明點解仲有咁多人妄想用正常途徑，例如法律，迫到佢交CCTV。<br />\n因為政府應該唔敢承擔打死人既後果，所以：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府一定唔會公佈＂打死左人＂既ＣＣＴＶ。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認為重點係擺係呢單野對群眾運動有咩影響，你可以話我地消費傷者，但實際上大家一路走來，大部份既升級行動都係建基於前幾日既警暴。<br />\n<br />\n呢單野如無意外應該石沉大海乜柒都查唔到，咁大家就會陷入左一種：有死人但係目擊者／証據比人滅左聲，然後時間慢慢沖淡。<br />\n<br />\n既然可以預料政府唔會公開ＣＣＴＶ，不如反客為主，<ins><strong>我覺得唯今之計係以大型示威行動去迫政府回應。用叫港鐵公開ＣＣＴＶ之名，去入機場去遊行去圍其他地方。</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>千祈唔好做一啲綁架高官然後同政府傾條件既行為，咁樣係唔岩架</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n不過，佢正常都會唔公開，咁就代表政府越黎越身有屎，咁樣先能夠利用到呢件事去激發更多民憤，要用公開831失蹤人士同查CCTV之名去舉行大型群眾運動先可以引起全世界關注，同埋借東風（傳媒）！<br />\n<br />\nP.S.我認為如果政府想隱暪，屍體有機會被特別安排或處理，未必送去殮房。你係政府都唔會咁戇鳩啦！一定係即刻鎖定＂現場已經知道既人士＂多一個人知道就越危險"},{"pid":"76c3e21ab8cf3977bdffc7ee410246abd20d998b","tid":1537494,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e6f9910fd8683287e7364dc28cb97bfa568ea6","tid":1537494,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n唔該入去幫p牌仔推一推 好人一世平安<br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f29386b8fc6a4a6dcdfdf0ea4aea9a75094a4f47","tid":1537494,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQ0Tyrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQ0Tyrc.jpg&h=d900eccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"77a3c2a33d42aa16d72b65b345a6d14b026a14dc","tid":1537494,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"１／１０"},{"pid":"bb3d2e290589f49213392dd335c211cc84